        <div type="level2">
         <head>On the use of these materials</head>
         <p>You might not be the kind of person that sits and read the guidelines page by page trying out new things. Or you might simply prefer another format or presentation.
         For these reasons, and to allow for a shared base of shared presentations, some of which originally based on the training materials
         of <ref target="https://wiki.digitalclassicist.org/EpiDoc_Workshops">EpiDoc</ref>,  we share here the training materials we have used, divided into programs and single presentations.
         The programs of each workshop will use a different selection of the presentations and at a different moment in the life of the project. Those presentations as they were given at that point
       will be linked in the programs, or only with the participants of that specific training, while the latest shareable version of a given presentation is linked below. </p>
</div>
